OL,3,CFormer footballer among four charged
OL,4,Cwith attempted murder
OL,6,FA former footballer has been charged
OL,7,Fwith attempted murder, along with
OL,8,Fthree others, after the shooting of a
OL,9,Fman on a driveway.
OL,11,FA man in his 20s was rushed to
OL,12,Fhospital in a critical condition on
OL,13,FFriday 28 November 2025 after being
OL,14,Fshot twice in the leg on a driveway on
OL,15,FRadway Road in Huyton.
OL,17,FOn Thursday 19 February, a number of
OL,18,Fwarrants were carried out across
OL,19,FKnowsley, Sefton and Liverpool and
OL,20,Ffour people were arrested.
