OL,6,FFormer Accrington Stanley midfielder
OL,7,Fand boxer Patrick Sean Lacey, 32, of
OL,8,FManor Avenue, Crosby, has now been
OL,9,Fcharged with attempted murder,
OL,10,Fconspiracy to murder, possession of
OL,11,Fshotgun and ammunition with intent to
OL,12,Fendanger life; section 18 GBH; and
OL,13,Fconspiracy to cause GBH.
OL,15,FJohn Aaron Jones, 35, of Stamfordham
OL,16,FDrive, Allerton, John George Patrick
OL,17,FHughes, 31, of no fixed abode, and
OL,18,FBernard Flynn, 61, of Knowsley Road,
OL,19,FBootle have also all been charged with
OL,20,Fthe above offences.
