OL,6,FDetective Inspector Chris Clark from
OL,7,Four Firearms Investigation Team said:
OL,8,F"These coordinated warrants were
OL,9,Fcarried out as part of an ongoing
OL,10,Finvestigation, and all four men will
OL,11,Fappear in court today.
OL,13,F"Our work continues, so I would ask
OL,14,Fthat people who have yet to come
OL,15,Fforward still do so. Please do not
OL,16,Fassume that we already hold
OL,17,Finformation.
